 By Fadekemi AjakaiyeProspective Nigerian investors in a real estate project in Dubai, promoted by Signature Global Real Estate, in collaboration with Sobha Realty of Dubai, UAE, have been promised zero tax investment opportunity. A statement by their media consultant, Siaka Momoh said there would be free fee consultancy service from one of Dubai’s top real estate consultant at the launch of their iconic project ‘Buy a Part of Dubai’ next week in Lagos. The grand event will hold at The George Hotel, 30 Lugard Avenue, Ikoyi.According to the statement m, “Exclusive benefits for participants are:Full insights about investment in Dubai. Eligibility to obtain a golden visa for yourself and family, and Dubai hospitality package.The event sponsors are Signature, Sobha Realty and Nigerian Indonesian Chamber of Commerce and Industry.